query:
SELECT s.id as studentId, s.registrationNumber, s.fullName, se.id as enrollmentId, se.subjectId, se.userId as professorId, sub.name as subjectName
FROM students s
LEFT JOIN subjectEnrollments se ON se.studentId = s.id
LEFT JOIN subjects sub ON sub.id = se.subjectId
WHERE s.registrationNumber = '2024001';
